[Student "S"]
{There is only one reason that SOUTH should not overcall with 1\S. He is too strong. 
The maximum strength of an overcall is 16 points. Above that you should double.

So SOUTH doubles, and after NORTH bids 2\C, SOUTH bids 2\S. This shows an overcall 
type hand, but with 17 or more points.

NORTH has fine trump support and 8 points so she bids a confident 4\S.}

